column15: In reference to the aforementioned agreement bearing no. AgrNoTest, the Respondent availed a loan facility from the Claimant. The Respondent committed an act of default by failing and neglecting to pay various amounts of instalments which fell due and payable in terms of the said agreement. In spite of reminders for the settlement of outstanding dues under the loan facility, the Respondent failed and neglected to pay the outstanding amount of Rs. 100000 as on 31-01-01 which till date remains outstanding and pending. Owing to the dispute that has arisen between the parties, the Claimant has invoked arbitration and seeks the following reliefs. 1
